-called van der Waals envelope\nare prevalent -- these interactions in particular pose an enormous challenge\nfor molecular modeling and are observed in many important chemical and\nbiological systems. A detailed SAPT-based energy decomposition analysis also\nconfirms the diverse and comprehensive nature of the intermolecular binding\nmotifs present in NENCI-2021.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Feb 2021 01:11:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-05"}
