ases and in synergy with\nsimulations, are fundamental to unravel the formation and evolution of the\nMilky Way discs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Feb 2021 14:47:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-05"}
